<!-- ============================================================================================
     BUNDLED OFAC SDN CRYPTO-ADDRESS SNAPSHOT (P8.7.3). A curated subset of REAL, public OFAC SDN
     "Digital Currency Address" designations, shipped so "Check intel" sanctions screening works fully
     OFFLINE out of the box. This is the APP's live bundled intel — it is DISTINCT from the tiny
     per-case validation fixtures under backend/tests/fixtures/ (those drive the make-smoke validation
     cases only and are never shipped as the app's intel source).

     NOT the complete current SDN list. Use Settings -> Intel sources -> "Refresh from source" to pull
     the full current sdn.xml from https://www.treasury.gov/ofac/downloads/sdn.xml.

     EDITION DATE = 01/15/2025 (Publish_Date below). Every address here was REAL and simultaneously on
     the OFAC SDN on that date. Sanctions are MUTABLE (Invariant #6 / the OFAC connector records each
     fetch as a dated observation and reports delistings): NOTABLY, **Tornado Cash was DELISTED from the
     SDN on 2025-03-21** (Fifth Circuit ruling, Treasury action) — it is included here because it was a
     valid designation as of this 2025-01-15 edition, and remains the canonical worked example of a
     sanctioned mixer. Refresh from source for the post-delisting current list.

     SOURCES (confirmed, CLAUDE.md §6, 2026-06-30):
       * Address->entity mapping: ultrasoundmoney/ofac-ethereum-addresses (data.csv) + 0xB10C/
         ofac-sanctioned-digital-currency-addresses (the documented machine-readable SDN extracts).
       * Tornado Cash designation (CYBER2, 2022-08-08; 38+ addresses): Treasury press release jy0916 +
         OFAC recent-actions/20220808. Anchor 0x722122dF...b6967 + Donate 0x8589...fda16 verified.
       * Garantex (RUSSIA-EO14024, 2022-04-05) + Hydra Market + Lazarus Group (Ronin) per OFAC.
     Only XBT (base58 BTC) and ETH (0x) tickers are bundled — the two chains BIH v1 canonicalizes.
     ============================================================================================ -->
